328655.こうげき力と かいしん率を\n上げる効果を付けられる。:
It is possible to add effects to increase the
attack power and critical rate.

328656.攻撃時に ヘナトスやルカニを\n付与する効果を付けられる。:
It is possible to add an effect that grants
Blunt or Sap when attacking.

328663.こうげき力を 上げる効果と\nＭＰ吸収ガードの 効果を付けられる。:
The effect of increasing attack power and the
effect of MP absorption guard can be added.

328664.呪文発動速度 呪文ぼうそう率と\nＭＰ消費しない率 ＭＰ吸収率を付けられる。\n:
Spell activation speed spellhaywire rate and
MP not consumed rate MP absorption rate can be
added. Can also increase stylishness.

328672.攻撃時に ヘナトスやルカニの効果を付けられる。\nどくばりなどに 攻撃時急所突き:
It can add Blunt and Sap effects to attacks,
and can also add a Stab effect to attacks such
as Poison Needle.

328679.盾ガード率と ブレス耐性を\n上げる効果を付けられる。:
The effect can be added to increase the shield
guard rate and breath resistance.

328680.攻撃呪文への耐性を上げる効果を 付けられる。\n呪いとしばりをガードする効果も付:
It can be added to increase resistance to
attack spells. It can also be added to guard
against curses and cloaks.

328687.最大ＨＰを 上げる効果を付けられる。:
The effect of increasing the maximum HP can be
added.

328688.最大ＭＰを上げる効果と\nさまざまなガード効果が付けられる。:
The effect of increasing maximum MP and
various guard effects can be added.

328695.しゅび力と ブレス耐性を\n上げる効果を付けられる。:
The effect can be added to increase the
ability to move and resistance to breath.

328696.こうげき魔力 かいふく魔力を上げる効果と\n攻撃呪文への耐性を上げる効果を付けら:
Attack Magic: This effect can be added to increase the healing magic power and resistance to attack spells. It can also be
used to guard against curses and instant death.

328703.しゅび力と ＭＰ吸収ガードを\n上げる効果を付けられる。:
The effect of increasing the guarding power
and MP absorption can be added.

328704.こうげき魔力 回復魔力を\n上げる効果が付けられる。\nさまざまなガード効果も付:
Attack Magic Recovery Magic Effects can be
added to increase recovery magic. Various
guard effects can also be added.

328711.きようさと かいしん率を\n上げる効果を付けられる。:
The effect of increasing deftness and critical
rate can be added.

328712.呪文発動速度 呪文ぼうそう率や\nＭＰ消費しない率を付けられる。\n攻撃時にヘナ:
Spell activation speed spellhaywire rate or
rate of not consuming MP can be added. Blunt
and sap effects can also be added to attacks.

328719.すばやさと おもさ 身かわし率を\n上げる効果を付けられる。:
The agility and weight effects can be added to
increase the dodging rate.

328720.踊りと転びを ガードする効果を付けられる。\nおしゃれさを上げることもできる。:
It can add an effect to guard against dancing
and falling. It can also increase
fashionability.
